HOLLYWOOD, Calif., Aug. 27 -- Lilli Palmer, absent from American films for several years, will be seen as the wife of Clark Gable in the romantic comedy, "But Not for Me." The actress is now in Munich, Germany. View Full Article in Timesmachine Â»
